                        <li>Dependency updates and vulnerability scanning during build.</li>
                        <li>Change management with rollback plans.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section id="vuln" class="mb-4" aria-labelledby="vuln-heading">
                    <h2 id="vuln-heading" class="h4">5. Vulnerability Management</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Regular patching of OS, runtime, and frameworks.</li>
                        <li>Routine security scans and remediation SLAs based on severity.</li>
                        <li>Bug reporting channel available to customers.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section id="incident" class="mb-4" aria-labelledby="incident-heading">
                    <h2 id="incident-heading" class="h4">6. Incident Response</h2>
                    <p>We maintain an incident response playbook: identification, containment, eradication, recovery, and post-incident review. Customers are notified of material incidents affecting their data.</p>
                </section>

                <section id="backup" class="mb-4" aria-labelledby="backup-heading">
                    <h2 id="backup-heading" class="h4">7. Backup & Disaster Recovery</h2>
